Crayon Development and Ultimus Holdings for the Indigo Residence Luxury Apartments project in Lagos. Classroom by Ultimus is set in the highbrow Victoria Island, Lagos, and is a delight of a growing clientele who have seen the difference between the informal and a very organised setup. It is a one-stop shop for everything exquisite ambiance fitting. The parent company is Ultimus Holdings, a pan-African investment company with interests in retail trading, real estate, construction, services and hospitality. Crayon Development is a start up real estate development company, taking a new approach to property development by building from the standpoint of the end user. The firm’s key focus is the functionality and efficiency of homes. They aim at  giving their end users the ultimate living experience. 